#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1742
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1761
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid "In case of slopes or obstacles in the way, the time is increased."
msgstr "Esant šlaitams ar kelyje esančioms kliūtims, laikas pailgėja."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Amazon production site: Woodcutter's
#. Hut
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1315
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid "Fells trees in the surrounding area and processes them into logs."
msgstr "kerta medžius apylinkėse ir apdoroja juos į rąstus."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for an Amazon production site: Woodcutter's Hut
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1317
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid "The woodcutter’s hut needs trees to fell within the work area."
msgstr "Medkirčių nameliui reikia medžių, kad jie nukristų į darbo vietą."

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for an Amazon production site:
#. Woodcutter's Hut, part 1
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1320
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid ""
"This building can produce one log between %1$s and %2$s (with master "
"woodcutter between %3$s and %4$s), depending on how far the woodcutter has "
"to walk."
msgstr "Šiame pastate galima pagaminti vieną rąstą nuo %1$s iki %2$s (su „Master Woodcutter“ nuo %3$s iki %4$s), priklausomai nuo to, kiek medžio pjovėjas turi nueiti."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Amazon production site: Jungle
#. Preserver's Hut
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1330
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid "Plants trees in the surrounding area."
msgstr "Apylinkėse sodina medžius."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for an Amazon production site: Jungle
#. Preserver's Hut
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1332
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid ""
"The jungle preserver’s hut needs free space within the work area to plant "
"the trees."
msgstr "Džiunglių saugotojo namelyje reikia laisvos vietos darbo zonoje medžiams sodinti."

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for an Amazon production site: Jungle
#. Preserver's Hut, part 1
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1335
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid ""
"The jungle preserver or jungle master plants one tree between %1$s and %2$s,"
" depending on how far she has to walk."
msgstr "Džiunglių konservatorius arba džiunglių meistras pasodina vieną medį nuo %1$s iki %2$s, priklausomai nuo to, kiek toli ji turi nueiti."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Amazon production site: Hunter-
#. Gatherer's Hut
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1345
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid "Hunts animals to produce meat. Catches fish in the waters."
msgstr "Medžioja gyvūnus, kad galėtų gaminti mėsą. Gauna žuvis vandenyse."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for an Amazon production site: Hunter-Gatherer's
#. Hut
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1348
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid ""
"The hunter-gatherer’s hut needs animals or fish to hunt or catch within the "
"work area."
msgstr "Medžiotojų-rinkėjo trobelėje reikia gyvūnų ar žuvų, kad galėtų medžioti ar gaudyti darbo vietoje."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for an Amazon production site: Hunter-Gatherer's
#. Hut
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1350
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid "Roads and trees along the shoreline block fishing."
msgstr "Keliai ir medžiai palei kranto liniją blokuoja žvejybą."

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for an Amazon production site: Hunter-
#. Gatherer's Hut, part 1
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1354
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid ""
"This building can produce one meat or one fish between %1$s and %2$s, "
"depending on how far the hunter-gatherer has to walk. If both kinds of food "
"are available, then one of each kind is produced between %3$s and %4$s."
msgstr "Šiame pastate galima užauginti vieną mėsą arba vieną žuvį nuo %1$s iki %2$s, priklausomai nuo to, kiek medžiotojas turi nueiti. Jei yra abiejų rūšių maisto, tada gaminamas vienas iš kiekvienos rūšies nuo %3$s iki %4$s ."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for an Amazon production site: Liana
#. Cutter's Hut
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1364
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid ""
"‘Sunlight smiled upon us and our Ancestors while we worked to clear liana "
"from the trees. I was not as efficient as my aunt and sisters, and so I "
"learned to ply rope.’"
msgstr "„Saulės šviesa nusišypsojo mums ir mūsų protėviams, kol stengėmės išvalyti Lianą nuo medžių. Aš nebuvau toks efektyvus kaip mano teta ir seserys, todėl išmokau važiuoti virve."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for an Amazon production site: Liana
#. Cutter's Hut
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1366
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid "Mistress WeaverSong, recollecting her early years as a liana cutter."
msgstr "Meilužė WeaverSong, prisimenanti savo ankstyvuosius lianų kirtėjos metus."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Amazon production site: Liana Cutter's
#. Hut
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1368
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid "Home of the liana cutter who cuts lianas for making ropes."
msgstr "Lianos katerio, kuris pjauna Lianas virvių gamybai, namai."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for an Amazon production site: Liana Cutter's
#. Hut
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1370
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid ""
"The liana cutter harvests liana from fully matured trees within the work "
"area which are not being used as lookouts."
msgstr "Liana kateris nuima Lianą iš visiškai subrendusių medžių darbo zonoje, kurie nėra naudojami kaip apžvalgos aikštelės."

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for an Amazon production site: Liana
#. Cutter's Hut, part 1
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1373
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid ""
"This building can produce one liana between %1$s and %2$s, depending on how "
"far the liana cutter has to walk."
msgstr "Šiame pastate gali būti pagaminta viena liana nuo %1$s iki %2$s, priklausomai nuo to, kiek Liana Cutter turi nueiti."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Amazon production site: Water
#. Gatherer's Hut
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1383
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid "Draws water out of the rivers and lakes."
msgstr "semia vandenį iš upių ir ežerų."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for an Amazon production site: Water Gatherer's
#. Hut, part 1
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1386
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid ""
"The water gatherer’s hut needs open water within the work area. Your workers"
" cannot dig up water from the ground!"
msgstr "Vandens rinkėjo trobelei darbo zonoje reikia atviro vandens. Jūsų darbuotojai negali iškasti vandens iš žemės!"

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for an Amazon production site: Water Gatherer's
#. Hut, part 2
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1388
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid "Roads and trees along the shoreline block drawing water."
msgstr "Keliai ir medžiai palei kranto bloką traukia vandenį."

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for an Amazon production site: Water
#. Gatherer's Hut, part 1
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1392
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid ""
"This building can produce one bucket of water between %1$s and %2$s on "
"average, depending on how far the carrier has to walk."
msgstr "Šis pastatas gali pagaminti vieną kibirą vandens nuo %1$s iki %2$s, priklausomai nuo to, kiek vežėjas turi nueiti."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Amazon production site: Rare Tree
#. Cutter's Hut
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1402
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid ""
"Harvests rare trees in the surrounding area. Delivers ironwood, balsa and "
"rubber."
msgstr "Nuima retus medžius apylinkėse. Tiekia geležies medieną, balsą ir gumą."

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for an Amazon production site: Rare Tree
#. Cutter's Hut, part 1
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1405
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid ""
"This building can produce one rare wood between %1$s and %2$s, depending on "
"how far the master woodcutter has to walk. If all kinds of rare tree are "
"available within her work area, then one of each kind is produced between "
"%3$s and %4$s."
msgstr "Šiame pastate galima pagaminti vieną retą medieną nuo %1$s iki %2$s, priklausomai nuo to, kiek toli turi nueiti medžio pjovėjas. Jei jos darbo zonoje yra visų rūšių retų medžių, tada vienas iš kiekvienos rūšies gaminamas nuo %3$s iki %4$s."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Amazon production site: Wilderness
#. Keeper's Tent
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1415
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid "Breeds fish and game to renew food resources."
msgstr "Veisia žuvis ir žvėrieną, kad atnaujintų maisto išteklius."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for an Amazon production site: Wilderness
#. Keeper's Tent
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1417
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid ""
"The wilderness keeper will only release new game at a nearby tree which is "
"not being used as a lookout."
msgstr "„Wilderness Keeper“ išleis naują žaidimą tik netoliese esančiame medyje, kuris nėra naudojamas kaip apžvalgos aikštelė."

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for an Amazon production site: Wilderness
#. Keeper's Tent, part 1
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1420
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid ""
"The wilderness keeper can breed one fish and release one animal between %1$s"
" and %2$s, depending on how far she has to walk."
msgstr "Laukinės gamtos prižiūrėtoja gali veisti vieną žuvį ir paleisti vieną gyvūną nuo %1$s iki %2$s, priklausomai nuo to, kiek ji turi nueiti."

#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1429
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid ""
"You need to connect this flag to a scout’s hut before you can send a scout "
"here."
msgstr "Turite prijungti šią vėliavą prie skautų trobelės, kad galėtumėte čia išsiųsti skautą."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Amazon production site: Scout's Hut
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1431
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid "Explores unknown territory."
msgstr "tyrinėja nežinomą teritoriją."

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for an Amazon production site: Scout's
#. Hut, part 1
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1434
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid "One exploration trip of the scout takes between %1$s and %2$s."
msgstr "Viena žvalgo kelionė trunka nuo %1$s iki %2$s."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for an Amazon production site: Rope
#. Weaver's Booth
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1446
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid ""
"‘My mother taught me to ply the ropes from Liana, how to choose the "
"strongest cuttings and parts of the harvest, how to trim away flaws. I bless"
" her wisdom in every length I use.’"
msgstr "„Mama išmokė mane apvynioti virves iš Lianos, kaip išsirinkti stipriausius auginius ir derliaus dalis, kaip pašalinti trūkumus. Aš laiminu jos išmintį visais mano naudojamais ilgiais."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for an Amazon production site: Rope
#. Weaver's Booth
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1448
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid "Mistress WeaverSong, reflecting on training."
msgstr "Mistress Weaversong, apmąstanti treniruotes."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Amazon production site: Rope Weaver's
#. Booth
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1450
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid "Makes ropes from lianas."
msgstr "Gamina virves iš Lianas."

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for an Amazon production site: Rope
#. Weaver's Booth
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1452
#, lua-format
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid "The rope weaver booth needs %s on average to produce one rope."
msgstr "„Rope Weaver“ kabinai vidutiniškai reikia %s, kad būtų pagaminta viena virvė."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Amazon production site: Furnace
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1459
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid "Smelts gold dust into gold ingots using charcoal."
msgstr "Naudodami anglį, aukso dulkes išlydo į aukso luitus."

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for an Amazon production site: Furnace
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1461
#, lua-format
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid ""
"The furnace can produce one gold ingot in %s on average if the supply is "
"steady."
msgstr "Jei tiekimas yra pastovus, krosnis gali pagaminti vidutiniškai vieną aukso luitą %s."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for an Amazon production site: Rare Tree
#. Plantation
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1468
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid ""
"‘If properly harvested, cured and stored, ironwood becomes almost "
"indestructible, and will not rust in damp conditions.’"
msgstr "„Jei tinkamai nuimama, sukietėja ir laikoma, geležies mediena tampa beveik nesunaikinama ir nerūdys drėgnomis sąlygomis."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for an Amazon production site: Rare Tree
#. Plantation
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1470
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid "Jungle Master Abacaxis"
msgstr "Džiunglių meistras Abacaxis"

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Amazon production site: Rare Tree
#. Plantation
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1472
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid ""
"Plants rare trees which are needed by the Amazons, like balsa, rubber and "
"ironwood."
msgstr "Pasodina retus medžius, kurių reikia amazonėms, pavyzdžiui, balsa, guma ir geležies mediena."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for an Amazon production site: Rare Tree
#. Plantation
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1474
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid ""
"Rare trees are planted according to the economy requirements. Keep roads "
"connected to rare tree plantations so they adhere to economy targets."
msgstr "Reti medžiai sodinami pagal ekonomikos reikalavimus. Laikykite kelius sujungtus su retomis medžių plantacijomis, kad jie atitiktų ekonominius tikslus."

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for an Amazon production site: Rare Tree
#. Plantation, part 1
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1477
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid ""
"The jungle master plants one tree between %1$s and %2$s, depending on how "
"far she has to walk."
msgstr "Džiunglių meistras pasodina vieną medį nuo %1$s iki %2$s, priklausomai nuo to, kiek toli ji turi nueiti."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Amazon production site: Stone Workshop
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1487
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid "Makes tools and spears for our soldiers."
msgstr "Gamina įrankius ir ietis mūsų kariams."

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for an Amazon production site: Stone
#. Workshop
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1489
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid ""
"If this building is fully supplied and all tools and spears are needed by "
"the economy, production of one of each tool takes %1$s and one of each spear"
" takes %2$s on average. If only one kind of tool or spear is needed by the "
"economy, its production takes %3$s on average."
msgstr "Jei šis pastatas yra visiškai aprūpintas ir visi įrankiai bei ietis reikalingi ekonomikai, vieno iš kiekvieno įrankio gamyba užtrunka %1$s, o viena iš kiekvienos ieties – vidutiniškai %2$s. Jei ekonomikai reikia tik vienos rūšies įrankio ar ieties, jos gamyba vidutiniškai užtrunka %3$s."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for an Amazon production site: Dressmakery
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1496
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid ""
"‘A skilled maker crafts garments of unsurpassed defence,<br> with each "
"stitch imbued with conscious intent.’"
msgstr "„Kvalifikuotas kūrėjas gamina nepralenktos gynybos drabužius,<br> su kiekvienu dygsniu, persmelktu sąmoningo ketinimo."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for an Amazon production site:
#. Dressmakery
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1498
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid ""
"Dressmakers’ ethos, adapted from the traditional verse ‘Mother Jungle’s "
"wisdom: Song of the Conscientious.’"
msgstr "siuvėjų etosas, pritaikytas iš tradicinės eilutės „Motinos džiunglių išmintis: sąžiningo daina“."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Amazon production site: Dressmakery
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1500
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid "Sews all dresses, boots and armor for our soldiers."
msgstr "Siuva visas sukneles, batus ir šarvus mūsų kariams."

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for an Amazon production site:
#. Dressmakery
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1502
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid ""
"If this building is fully supplied and all dresses, boots and armors are "
"needed by the economy, production of one of each of them takes %1$s on "
"average. If only one kind of them is needed by the economy, its production "
"takes %2$s on average."
msgstr "Jei šis pastatas yra pilnai aprūpintas, o ekonomikai reikalingi visi sukneliai, batai ir šarvai, kiekvieno iš jų gamyba vidutiniškai užtrunka %1$s. Jei ekonomikai reikia tik vienos rūšies jų, jos gamyba vidutiniškai užtrunka %2$s."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Amazon production site: Charcoal Kiln
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1509
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid "Burns logs into charcoal."
msgstr "Sudegina rąstus į anglį."

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for an Amazon production site: Charcoal
#. Kiln
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1511
#, lua-format
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid "The charcoal kiln needs %s on average to produce one lump of coal."
msgstr "Anglies krosnyje vidutiniškai reikia %s, kad susidarytų vienas anglies luitas."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Amazon production site: Cassava Root
#. Cooker
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1518
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid "Bakes bread from cassava root."
msgstr "Kepa duoną iš maniokos šaknies."

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for an Amazon production site: Cassava
#. Root Cooker
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1520
#, lua-format
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid ""
"If all needed wares are delivered in time, this building can produce one "
"bread in %s on average."
msgstr "Jei visi reikalingi gaminiai pristatomi laiku, šis pastatas gali pagaminti vidutiniškai vieną duoną %s."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Amazon production site: Chocolate
#. Brewery
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1527
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid "Brews chocolate for soldier training."
msgstr "gamina šokoladą kareivių mokymui."

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for an Amazon production site: Chocolate
#. Brewery
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1529
#, lua-format
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid ""
"The chocolate brewery needs %s on average to brew one mug of chocolate."
msgstr "Šokoladinei alaus daryklai vidutiniškai reikia %s, kad išvirtų vieną puodelį šokolado."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Amazon production site: Food Preserver
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1536
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid ""
"Prepares rations to feed the scouts and the workers digging for gold dust "
"and granite."
msgstr "Paruošia racioną, kad pamaitintų skautus ir darbuotojus, kasdamas aukso dulkes ir granitą."

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for an Amazon production site: Food
#. Preserver
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1538
#, lua-format
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid ""
"The food preserver can produce one ration in %s on average if the supply is "
"steady."
msgstr "Maisto konservatorius gali pagaminti vidutiniškai vieną racioną %s, jei tiekimas yra pastovus."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Amazon production site: Initiation
#. Site
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1545
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid "Equips recruits and trains them as soldiers."
msgstr "aprūpina juos ir apmoko juos kaip karius."

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for an Amazon production site: Initiation
#. Site
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1547
#, lua-format
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid "The initiation site needs %s on average to recruit one soldier."
msgstr "Iniciacijos vietai reikia vidutiniškai %s, kad būtų įdarbintas vienas karys."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Amazon production site: Gardening
#. Center
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1554
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid "Enhances the fertility of the landscape for trees."
msgstr "Padidina kraštovaizdžio derlingumą medžiams."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for an Amazon production site: Gardening Center
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1556
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid ""
"Only a Jungle Master has the necessary experience to coax more growth from "
"land."
msgstr "Tik džiunglių meistras turi reikiamos patirties, kad paskatintų daugiau augimo iš žemės."

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for an Amazon production site: Gardening
#. Center, part 1
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1559
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid ""
"The jungle master can perform one terraform between %1$s and %2$s, depending"
" on how far she has to walk."
msgstr "Džiunglių meistras gali atlikti vieną reljefo formą nuo %1$s iki %2$s, priklausomai nuo to, kiek ji turi nueiti."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Amazon production site: Tapir Farm
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1571
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid "Breeds tapirs for adding them to the transportation system."
msgstr "Veisia tapyrus, kad įtrauktų juos į transportavimo sistemą."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for an Amazon production site: Tapir Farm
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1573
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid "Tapirs help to prevent traffic jams on highly used roads."
msgstr "Tapyrai padeda išvengti kamščių labai naudojamuose keliuose."

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for an Amazon production site: Tapir Farm
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1575
#, lua-format
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid ""
"If all needed wares are delivered in time, this building can produce a tapir"
" in %s on average."
msgstr "Jei visi reikalingi gaminiai pristatomi laiku, šis pastatas gali pagaminti vidutiniškai %s."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Amazon production site: Cassava
#. Plantation
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1582
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid "Sows and harvests cassava."
msgstr "sėja ir nuima manioką."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for an Amazon production site: Cassava
#. Plantation
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1584
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid ""
"The cassava plantation needs free space within the work area to plant seeds."
msgstr "Kasavos plantacijai reikia laisvos vietos darbo zonoje sėkloms sodinti."

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for an Amazon production site: Cassava
#. Plantation, part 1
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1587
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid ""
"The cassava farmer sows and harvests one bundle of cassava between %1$s and "
"%2$s, depending on how far she has to walk."
msgstr "Maniokos augintojas sėja ir nuima vieną maniokos ryšulį nuo %1$s iki %2$s, priklausomai nuo to, kiek toli ji turi nueiti."

#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1589
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1604
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/atlanteans/units.lua:1839
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/atlanteans/units.lua:1857
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/barbarians/units.lua:1320
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/barbarians/units.lua:1549
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/empire/units.lua:1574
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/empire/units.lua:1800
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/frisians/units.lua:1675
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/frisians/units.lua:2081
#, lua-format
msgid "%d growing field"
msgid_plural "%d growing fields"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""
msgstr[2] ""
msgstr[3] ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for an Amazon production site: Cassava
#. Plantation, part 2; %s is replaced by 'N growing fields'
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1589
#, lua-format
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid ""
"The cassava plantation needs at least %s to work at full productivity most "
"of the time."
msgstr "Maniokos plantacijai reikia bent %s, kad didžiąją laiko dalį veiktų visu produktyvumu."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Amazon production site: Cocoa Farm
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1597
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid "Cultivates cocoa that is needed to brew chocolate drinks."
msgstr "Augina kakavą, reikalingą šokoladiniams gėrimams virti."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for an Amazon production site: Cocoa Farm
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1599
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid "Chocolate is essential for training Amazon soldiers."
msgstr "Šokoladas yra būtinas mokant „Amazon“ karius."

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for an Amazon production site: Cocoa
#. Farm, part 1
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1602
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid ""
"The cocoa farmer sows and harvests one basket of cocoa beans between %1$s "
"and %2$s, depending on how far she has to walk."
msgstr "Kakavos augintojas sėja ir nuima vieną krepšį kakavos pupelių nuo %1$s iki %2$s, priklausomai nuo to, kiek ji turi nueiti."

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for an Amazon production site: Cocoa
#. Farm, part 2; %s is replaced by 'N growing fields'
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1604
#, lua-format
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid ""
"The cocoa farm needs at least %s to work at full productivity most of the "
"time."
msgstr "Kakavos ūkiui reikia bent %s, kad didžiąją laiko dalį dirbtų visu produktyvumu."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Amazon production site: Stone Mine
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1614
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid "Digs granite and quartz out of the ground in mountain terrain."
msgstr "Kasa granitą ir kvarcą iš žemės kalnų vietovėje."

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for an Amazon production site: Stone Mine
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1616
#, lua-format
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid ""
"The stone mine can produce one slab of each kind of stone in %s on average "
"if the supply with rations is steady and the mine is not worn out."
msgstr "Akmens kasykla gali pagaminti po vieną plokštę kiekvienos rūšies akmens vidutiniškai %s, jei tiekimas su racionu yra pastovus ir kasykla nėra susidėvėjusi."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Amazon production site: Gold Digger
#. Dwelling
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1623
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid "Washes gold dust out of the ground in mountain terrain."
msgstr "Išplauna aukso dulkes iš žemės kalnų vietovėje."

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for an Amazon production site: Gold
#. Digger Dwelling
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1625
#, lua-format
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid ""
"If the supply is steady, this mine can produce gold dust in %s on average."
msgstr "Jei tiekimas yra pastovus, ši kasykla gali gaminti aukso dulkes vidutiniškai %s."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Amazon training site: Warriors’
#. Gathering
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1634
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid ""
"Trains soldiers in Attack up to level 2. Equips the soldiers with all "
"necessary weapons."
msgstr "Apmoko karius puolime iki 2 lygio. aprūpina karius visais reikalingais ginklais."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for an Amazon training site: Warriors’ Gathering
#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for an Amazon training site: Training Glade
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1636
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1651
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid "Amazon soldiers need chocolate to train properly."
msgstr "„Amazon“ kariams reikia šokolado, kad galėtų tinkamai treniruotis."

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for an Amazon training site: Warriors’
#. Gathering, part 1
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1639
#, lua-format
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid ""
"If all needed wares are delivered in time, a warriors’ gathering can train "
"one soldier one level in attack in %s on average."
msgstr "Jei visi reikalingi gaminiai pristatomi laiku, „Warriors“ susirinkimas gali išmokyti vieną karį vieno lygio puolime vidutiniškai %s."

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for an Amazon training site: Warriors’
#. Gathering, part 2
#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for an Amazon training site: Training
#. Glade, part 2
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1641
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1656
#, lua-format
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid "Complete training of one soldier takes %s on average."
msgstr "Visiškas vieno kario mokymas vidutiniškai užtrunka %s."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Amazon training site: Training Glade
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1649
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid ""
"Trains soldiers in Evade, Defense and Health. Equips the soldiers with all "
"necessary equipment and armor parts."
msgstr "Apmoko karius išsisukinėti, gynybą ir sveikatą. aprūpina karius visa reikalinga įranga ir šarvų dalimis."

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for an Amazon training site: Training
#. Glade, part 1
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1654
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid ""
"If all needed wares are delivered in time, a training glade can train one "
"soldier to the first level in evade or health, or both defense levels in "
"%1$s on average. The rest of evade and health levels are trained in %2$s "
"each."
msgstr "Jei visi reikalingi gaminiai pristatomi laiku, treniruočių laukelis gali išmokyti vieną karį į pirmąjį „Evade“ ar „Health“ lygį arba abu gynybos lygius vidutiniškai %1$s. Likę „Evade“ ir „Health“ lygiai yra mokomi %2$s."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Amazon military site: Patrol Post
#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Amazon military site: Treetop Sentry
#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Amazon military site: Warriors’
#. Dwelling
#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Amazon military site: Tower
#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Amazon military site: Observation
#. Tower
#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Amazon military site: Fortress
#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Amazon military site: Fortification
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1666
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1675
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1684
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1693
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1702
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1711
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1720
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid "Garrisons soldiers to expand your territory."
msgstr "Garnizonų kariai, kad išplėstų jūsų teritoriją."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for an Amazon military site: Patrol Post
#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for an Amazon military site: Warriors’ Dwelling
#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for an Amazon military site: Tower
#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for an Amazon military site: Observation Tower
#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for an Amazon military site: Fortress
#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for an Amazon military site: Fortification
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1668
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1686
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1695
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1704
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1713
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1722
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid ""
"If you’re low on soldiers to occupy new military sites, use the downward "
"arrow button to decrease the capacity. You can also click on a soldier to "
"send her away."
msgstr "Jei jums trūksta kareivių, kad galėtumėte užimti naujas karines vietas, naudokite rodyklės žemyn mygtuką, kad sumažintumėte pajėgumus. Taip pat galite spustelėti kareivį, kad ją išsiųstumėte."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for an Amazon military site: Treetop Sentry
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1677
msgctxt "amazons_building"
