#. Yard, part 1
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1740
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid ""
"This building can produce one ferry between %1$s and %2$s, depending on how "
"far the shipwright has to walk."
msgstr "Šis pastatas gali nutiesti vieną keltą nuo %1$s iki %2$s, priklausomai nuo to, kiek toli laivų meistras turi nueiti."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Amazon production site: Shipyard
#: ../../../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:1750
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid ""
"Constructs ships that are used for overseas colonization and for trading "
"between ports."
msgstr "Konstruoja laivus, kurie naudojami užjūrio kolonizacijai ir prekybai tarp uostų."

